    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Christmas Blaster:</h2> Christmas Blaster is an Arcade-type action video game. Santa needs to save Christmas and face creatures and his enemy Krampus with a lot of blast in this fun action-packed game. Inspired by games from the 80's and 90's. It's a dual-stick shooter in the same vein as Robotron: 2084 from 1982, Smash TV from 1990, Hyper Princess Pitch(Daniel Remar) 2011. The game was thought to be faithful in its original art, mechanics, soundtrack and sound effects and has a password system to record progress, faithfully following the games of the time and can also be played by up to 4 players on the same screen.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2120240/extras/5b1ed5d757bed4974d4e88989fa3db78.poster.avif?t=1734200635\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2120240/extras/5b1ed5d757bed4974d4e88989fa3db78.webm?t=1734200635\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2120240/extras/5b1ed5d757bed4974d4e88989fa3db78.mp4?t=1734200635\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >GamePlay:</h2>Go solo or [you join co-op] and fight in the dark depths of the North Pole, where the dreaded Krampus lives, surviving a challenging and evolving series of assets filled with hand-built dangers and lovable, fearsome enemies. . . Use the classic controller type or switch to dual-stick and have a new experience!",
